original_title: Nine People Hospitalized From Wasp Attack In Madolsima Mini Worlds End
original_body_lines: COLOMBO (News 1st); Nine people were hospitalized following a wasps attack in Madolsima Mini Worlds End. Police said that the group had come from Gampaha on a trip when the incident occurred.The group had been spending the night in tents. Authorities confirmed that the injured have been admitted to the Lunugala Hospital.
